@prefix dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix dcat: <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix ids: <https://w3id.org/idsa/core/> .
@prefix idsc: <https://w3id.org/idsa/code/> .
@prefix idsm: <https://w3id.org/idsa/metamodel/> .
@prefix sh: <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#> .
@prefix shapes: <https://github.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/> .


shapes:DurationAgreementTemplateShape
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:targetClass ids:DurationAgreement ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationAgreementTemplate-permissionPropertyShape ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationAgreementTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationAgreementTemplateShape): In a _:DurationAgreement the ids:provider property must point to exactly one participant and the ids:consumer property must point to exactly one participant. This can in any case be a) an IRI or b) an ids:Participant. The ids:permission property must point to at exactly one ids:Permission. In the ids:Permission the ids:assigner, ids:assignee, ids:target and ids:action properties have to be specified. The ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with ids:leftOperand idsc:ELAPSED_TIME, ids:operator idsc:SHORTER_EQ and ids:rightOperand pointing xsd:duration specifying the duration of the agreement."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationAgreementTemplate-permissionPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:permission ;
    sh:class ids:Permission ;
    sh:node shapes:DurationAgreementPermissionTemplate ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:maxCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationAgreementTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationAgreementTemplate-permissionPropertyShape): In a _:DurationAgreement the ids:permission property must point to at exactly one ids:Permission. In the ids:Permission the ids:assigner, ids:assignee, ids:target and ids:action properties have to be specified. The ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with ids:leftOperand idsc:ELAPSED_TIME, ids:operator idsc:SHORTER_EQ and ids:rightOperand pointing xsd:duration specifying the duration of the agreement."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationAgreementPermissionTemplate
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:property shapes:AgreementPermissionTemplate-assignerPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:AgreementPermissionTemplate-assigneePropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:PermissionTemplate-targetPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:PermissionTemplate-actionPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationPermissionTemplate-constraintPropertyShape ;
.


shapes:DurationPermissionTemplate-constraintPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:constraint ;
    sh:class ids:Constraint ;
    sh:node shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplateShape ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationAgreementTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationPermissionTemplate-constraintPropertyShape): In an ids:DurationAgreement/-Offer/-Request within the ids:Permission the ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with ids:leftOperand idsc:ELAPSED_TIME, ids:operator idsc:SHORTER_EQ and ids:rightOperand pointing xsd:duration specifying the duration of the agreement."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplateShape
    a sh:NodeShape ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-leftOperandPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-operatorPropertyShape ;
    sh:property shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-rightOperandPropertyShape ;
.


shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-leftOperandPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:leftOperand ;
    sh:hasValue idsc:ELAPSED_TIME ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:maxCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationAgreementTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-leftOperandPropertyShape): In an ids:DurationAgreement/-Offer/-Request within the ids:Permission the ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with an ids:leftOperand property pointing to the value idsc:ELAPSED_TIME."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-operatorPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:operator ;
    sh:hasValue idsc:SHORTER_EQ ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:maxCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationAgreementTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-operatorPropertyShape): In an ids:DurationAgreement/-Offer/-Request within the ids:Permission the ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with an ids:operator property pointing to the value idsc:SHORTER_EQ."@en ;
.


shapes:DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-rightOperandPropertyShape
    a sh:PropertyShape ;
    sh:path ids:rightOperand ;
    sh:datatype xsd:duration ;
    sh:minCount 1 ;
    sh:maxCount 1 ;
    sh:severity sh:Violation ;
    sh:message "<https://raw.githubusercontent.com/International-Data-Spaces-Association/InformationModel/master/examples/contract-and-usage-policy/templates/TimeRestrictedUsageTemplates/DurationAgreementTemplateShape.ttl> (DurationPermissionConstraintTemplate-rightOperandPropertyShape): In an ids:DurationAgreement/-Offer/-Request within the ids:Permission the ids:constraint property must point to an ids:Constraint with an ids:rightOperand property pointing to a xsd:duration specifying the duration of the agreement."@en ;
.
